00:21:33.660 --> 00:21:34.950
que d'accomplir ma mission !

00:21:37.960 --> 00:21:43.130
Big Brother Tai l'a enfin fait !
Nous, les pirates d'Arlong, allons

00:21:43.130 --> 00:21:46.300
